Name: Dark Zone Defense
About the game: Dark Zone Defense is an exciting mix of classic arcade shooter and rogue-lite. The game is small but very challenging !!! Every thing in game is unique, so every time you restart, you'll have new feelings and situation. Game features: - No movement, surrounded by the darkness - 20+ guns, 50+ skills and abilities that can generate hundreds of play styles - Tons of monsters - Powerful Bosses - Steam Leaderboard - 5-20 minute game sessions The dark and challenging world is waiting for you! ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ This is my first indie game that I solo made, I hope you will like it. Thank you for any advice and comments.
